@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Vest respects your privacy. We may collect basic information such as your name, email address, account details, and usage data (like device information and activity on the platform) to provide, maintain, and improve our services. If transactions are processed through Vest, payment information is handled securely by third-party providers, and we do not store full payment card details.

We do not sell your personal information. Your data may be shared only with trusted service providers (such as hosting or payment processors) or when required by law. We take reasonable security measures to protect your information, and you may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your data at any time by contacting us.</p>
